NG0514:5: 'khor 'das mtha' grol klong du phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0514:6: sems can tshe lo 'bum gyi dus //
NG0514:8: drod dang gsher gyis gnas su bstan //
NG0514:9: chags pa logs can 'dul ba'i phyir //
NG0514:10: thabs kyi rgyud las skyed bskyed pa'i //
NG0514:11: byang chub sems dpa' 'brug sgrog drug / rigs ldan 'khor brdal bka' stsal ba //
NG0514:13: dbang gsum gnad gsum gzer gdab pas //
NG0514:14: bsdod gsum tshad gsum yul gsum chod //
NG0514:15: zhing khams gsum la longs spyod pas //
NG0514:16: ngo sprod gsum gyis thag chod cig / ces gsungs so //
NG0514:17: 'khor ba dong sprugs gser gyi 'bru gcig pa zhes bya ba /
NG0514:18: thugs rje dreg grol sa ma ya rgya rgya rgya /
NG0514:19: sngags kyi bdag mos srungs cig / gter rgya /
